    <metadata>

      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">

          <identifier>

          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">American Leaders Speak: Recordings from World War I and the 1920 Election, 1918-1920</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Amerikanische Führer Sprechen: Aufnahmen 
vom Ersten Weltkrieg und von der 1920 Wahl, 1918-1920</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Chefs Américains Parlent : 
Enregistrements de la Première Guerre Mondiale et 1920 de 
l'élection, 1918-1920</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Os Líderes Americanos Falam: Gravações do
world.war.i e 1920 da eleição, 1918-1920</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">I Capi Americani Parlano: 
Registrazioni dal world.war.i e 1920 dall'elezione, 1918-1920</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Οι αμερικανικοί ηγέτες μιλούν: Καταγραφές από 
τον παγκόσμιο πόλεμο Ι και η εκλογή του 1920, 1918-1920</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Los Arranques de cinta Americanos Hablan: 
Grabaciones de la Primera Guerra Mundial y 1920 de la elección,
1918-1920</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">consists of 59 sound recordings of speeches by American leaders at the turn of the century. Speakers include Warren G. Harding, James Cox, Calvin Coolidge, Franklin D. Roosevelt, Samuel Gompers, Henry Cabot Lodge, and John J. Pershing.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">besteht aus 59 Tonaufnahmen von Reden durch 
American Führer an der Jahrhundertwende. Lautsprecher enthalten
Warren G. Harding, James Cox, Calvin Coolidge, Franklin D. Roosevelt, 
Samuel Gompers, Henry Cabot Hütte und John J. Pershing.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">se compose de 59 enregistrements sonores des 
discours par des amorces d'American à la fin du siècle. Les 
orateurs incluent Warren G. Harding, James Cox, Calvin Coolidge,
Franklin D. Roosevelt, Samuel Gompers, loge de Cabot d'Henry, et John 
J. Pershing.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">consiste em 59 gravações sadias dos discursos 
por líderes de Americano na volta do século. Os altofalantes 
incluem Warren G. Harding, James Cox, Calvin Coolidge, Franklin D. 
Roosevelt, Samuel Gompers, alojamento de Cabot do Henry, e John J. 
Pershing.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">consiste di 59 registrazioni del suono dei 
discorsi dai capi dell'American alla fine del secolo. Gli
altoparlanti includono Warren G. Harding, James Cox, Calvin Coolidge, 
Franklin D. Roosevelt, Samuel Gompers, casetta di Cabot di henry e 
John J. Pershing.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">αποτελείται από 59 υγιείς καταγραφές των ομιλιών 
των αμερικανικών ηγετών στο γύρισμα του αιώνα. Οι ομιλητές 
περιλαμβάνουν Warren Γ. Harding, james Cox, Calvin 
Coolidge, Franklin Δ. Roosevelt, το Samuel Gompers, 
Henry Cabot Lodge, και John J. Pershing.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">consiste en 59 grabaciones de sonidos de discursos
de los arranques de cinta american al final del siglo. Los 
altavoces incluyen a Warren G. Harding, a James Cox, a Calvin 
Coolidge, a Franklin D. Roosevelt, a Samuel Gompers, casa de campo de 
Cabot del Henrio, y a Juan J. Pershing.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
